TIME:             09h00 



VENUE:         Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Parliament, Cape Town 





NB: There will be a video link to Ronnie Mamoepa Media Centre, Tshedimosetso House, 1035 Francis Baard Str. Hatfield, Pretoria





